- Moved `tracing:fastify.request.handler:error` publication to after error handling in `lib/handle-request.js` and `lib/wrap-thenable.js`, so subscribers see the final reply status instead of the default `200`.
- Added a regression test for the nested `setErrorHandler` case from the issue: `test/diagnostics-channel/error-status-from-handler.test.js`.

